    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "UNKNOWN OBJECT OVER OAK RIDGE, TENNESSEE, MARCH 1, 1950",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "[REDACTED] INFORMANT",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "VITAL FACILITIES",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "INTERNAL SECURITY",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] operator of [REDACTED], Knoxville, is",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "reported to have detected on his radar equipment an object directly over Oak",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Ridge, Tennessee, at an altitude of 40,000 feet at 11:15 p. m., March 1, 1950.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "On March 2, 1950, he advised that his radar equipment recorded an object about",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "100,000 feet high and approximately 15 miles from his home in Knoxville at 11:15",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "a. m. on that date. It was reported that Naval Reserve radar equipment at Knoxville,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Tennessee, did not detect an object on any occasion but stated that the equipment",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "was not considered efficient for aircraft at extreme altitudes. It was further",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "reported that qualified persons at Oak Ridge, questioned [REDACTED] and examined his",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "radar equipment. They reportedly found his equipment not too reliable and felt",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "that [REDACTED] was technically wrong on some of his radar theory. The reliability",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "of [REDACTED] was also questioned due to some degree of inebriation.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "No investigation is being conducted by this Bureau but in the event",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "additional information comes to our attention you will be promptly advised.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "KWD:eal:mes",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
